FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  >  2 AND t.production_year  =  2004 AND ci.person_id  <  2312693 AND mk.keyword_id  <  81220
